      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated double-VANOS system for peak volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by upgraded bushings and performance-tuned dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain optimal geometry under load. A mechanically sound example ready for the technical driver.",
