      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Premium All-Road SUV that perfectly balances luxury with daily utility. This vehicle is in solid, dependable condition and has been a reliable family companion. The exterior finished in Metallic Graphite remains lustrous, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper. Mechanically, this car is sound; it has followed a strict maintenance schedule with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The 2.0L turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. We recently replaced the front brake pads and rotors, and the all-season tires currently retain about 60% of their tread life. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with charcoal leather upholstery. The seats are plush and supportive, though the driver\u2019s side bolster shows light natural creasing from entry and exit. Every electronic feature\u2014from the panoramic sunroof to the premium 10-speaker sound system and heated seats\u2014functions exactly as it should. It\u2019s a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy without immediate worry.",
